prompt: A serene Japanese garden with cherry blossom trees and a koi pond
revised_prompt: Imagine a serene Japanese garden. In its tranquil spaces, appreciate the soft hues of cherry blossom trees in full bloom, casting a shower of gentle pink petals on a well-trodden stone path. Near this path, discover a koi pond, where multi-colored fishes swim lazily, adding a splash of dynamic color to the tranquil scene. Balanced rock formations, a symbol of harmony, are also present, subtly incorporated within the landscape. In the background, a traditional Japanese tea house with its unique architecture provides a resting spot amidst all this natural beauty.
